  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introdução a yasm</title>

    <para>
      <application>Yasm</application> is a complete rewrite of the <xref
linkend="nasm"/> assembler. It supports the x86 and AMD64 instruction sets,
accepts NASM and GAS assembler syntaxes and outputs binary, ELF32 and ELF64
object formats.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

